Title: Dookudu
Writer: Gopimohan (story), Upendra Madhav (Associate Writer), Kona Venkat (dialogue)
Actors: Mahesh Babu, Samantha Ruth Prabhu, Sonu Sood, Srinivasa Rao Kota
Plot: Ajay, (Mahesh Babu) an undercover cop, is assigned to catch a dangerous mafia don with whom he has a personal score to settle.
